ygData.subject: RE: Blackened Iron Bastard Sword?
ygData.msgSnippet: Depends on what you mean as Mid-Level. True Mid level, like 25-30, yeah, I think it s really good. You can find low level goblins (green to a 12th leveler),
ygData.messageBody:
Depends on what you mean as Mid-Level. True Mid level, like 25-30, yeah, I
think it's really good. You can find low level goblins (green to a 12th
leveler), and everything else is like 18-20+. Not much in the middle of
that.

As far as the BIBS, sorry, not sure. I *think* it's on the goblin chieftain
o king, whatever, but, really, I'm making that up. I don't honestly know.
Heh...

-Zantaer/Leod, Fennin Ro

-----Original Message-----
From: Sean.Clark@... [mailto:Sean.Clark@...]
Sent: Friday, July 16, 1999 10:26 AM
To: EQCheats@onelist.com
Subject: [EQCheats] Blackened Iron Bastard Sword?


From: Sean.Clark@...


Hiya all!
I'm lookin for some info (*spoil* me, PLEASE!) on the BIBS. I know its in
Runneyeye, but was looking for more specifics on the location, the MOB that
carries it, group lvl needed to get to / obtain the sword, etc, etc. I
haven't spent much time in Runneyeye...is it a good mid-level dungeon? it
doesn't seem very crowded..which would be a NICE change after spending the
last week in Unrest!
Also, for those of you wise in the way of Runneyeye...what MOBs drop the
Blackened Iron armor pieces? I know the AC isn't great, and it weighs a
lot, but it looks very cool and I bet there is a market out there for that
'look'.
Thanks in advance for your help!!
Thoradin of Bristlebane
